HackerNews Plus
A Google Chrome Addon to make the HackerNews experience a little better.

Developer: Mayank Singhal
GiitHub ID: mayanksinghal


v0.1.1
Fixed Bug: Works on Landing Page.

v0.1.0
Basic Keyboard shortcuts
   k - Previous Story
   j - Next Story
   Home - First Story
   End - Last Story (or More)
   m - Open Story in Current Window
   n - Open Story in New Window
   Return - Open Story in Current Window
   Shift + Return - Open Story in New Window
